-- Jury convicts Brocade ex-CEO in options trial
-- 
-- Tue Aug 7, 2007 3:05pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/08/07/us-brocade-conviction-idUSN0724543320070807

 

 SAN FRANCISCO  (Reuters) - A U.S. jury convicted the former chief executive of Brocade Communications Systems Inc ( BRCD.O ) on all 10 counts on Tuesday in the government's first criminal options-backdating trial. 

